description:
ONAY! — a transport app for residents and visitors of Almaty, Karaganda, Saran, Balkhash, Temirtau, Taldykorgan, and Ust-Kamenogorsk.

Your Daily Assistant For:
Real-Time Public Transport Tracking:
•	Plan your time by tracking buses/trolleybuses in real time;
•	Build routes using stops and points on the map;
•	View route schematics for all transport types;
•	Add frequent routes to Favorites for quick access;
•	Check transport operator info by tapping vehicle icons;
•	See estimated arrival times by selecting stop icons;


ONAY! Card Management:
•	Activate a free virtual ONAY! card;
•	Pay fares by, scanning transport QR codes and manually entering vehicle codes;
•	Purchase tickets for others via "Buy More" button;
•	Instantly top up your card balance;
•	Enable Auto-Topup for seamless balance management;
•	Review ride history;
•	Manage family/friends' cards: track balances + top up remotely;
•	Purchase travel passes;
•	Block lost/stolen cards instantly;
•	Add home screen widgets for key functions;

Accessibility Features:
•	Full VoiceOver screen reader support for visually impaired users;

In-App Marketplace (Almaty, Astana, Karaganda):
•	Access via "Shop" in bottom menu;
•	Discover one-click purchases for diverse products;

Support Contacts (6:30 AM – 11:00 PM):
• Almaty / Taldykorgan: +7 (727) 397 01 91, +7 (777) 397 01 91
• Karaganda / Saran / Balkhash / Temirtau: +7 (7212) 50 60 50, +7 (777) 397 01 91
• Ust-Kamenogorsk: +7 (777) 397 01 91


Technical Issues?
Email: info@onay.kz
Your feedback drives our improvements!

FlyArystan - affordable air tickets on your phone. The ability to search for a flight, select, order, book and buy plane tickets online. Price and cost for the flight - choose what the best is for you.

When starting the application, you select the place of departure and arrival, and indicate the required dates and the number of passengers. The system generates, based on requests, available aircraft and current prices for the flight. Next, you need to select the fare: Standard, Standard Plus, Comfort, Comfort Plus, depending on the amount of baggage carried. After filling in all the required fields, you have boarding passes for flights. The next step is to fill in information about yourself.

The My Booking section displays all previously purchased tickets. There is no need to worry and remember about the time, aircraft number and seat, because everything is already on the phone.

Separately, there is also a Check-In online section. Save time and check in for your flight online in just a couple of clicks, it is free, securely and quickly.

The FlyArystan app has the ability to:
•	check the status of flights;
•	news about profitable destinations;
•	discounts and promotions, vouchers;
•	a varied menu selection during the flight;
•	convenient flights booking;
•	flights prices;
•	seat selection;
•	take a ticket on credit for certain periods (3, 6, 12 or 24 months);

The mobile check-in service is also available for passengers with special needs.

The Booking Confirmation is also available in a convenient PDF format; you can use it both from your phone and print a paper version. Early baggage booking saves up to 70%.

FlyArystan is the best assistant when buying airplane tickets in Kazakhstan. Download the app and see for yourself. FlyArystan is a reliable and convenient air carrier of high quality!

